abstract: Last weekend, in a family thing, we went to see the new movie "Sex in the City." As I cringed over what seemed a celebration of banal excess, my 19-year-old daughter, beaming, was loving it.
lead_paragraph: Last weekend, in a family thing, we went to see the new movie "Sex in the City." As I cringed over what seemed a celebration of banal excess, my 19-year-old daughter, beaming, was loving it.

abstract: Hillary, you’ve been a great candidate, better than your train-wreck campaign. But now it’s time for you to try to muster a gracious exit.
